{"tid":426500,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"孝子問抽油煙機邊隻好","createTime":"2017-10-06T15:57:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T16:27:07.000Z","uid":7576,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"de0acc44b7fec1989a147fc86701cc6ae8ff4780","tid":426500,"uid":7576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:57:34.000Z","msg":"屋企抽油煙機唔夠勁<br />\n媽媽煮飯成日吸到油煙<br />\n邊隻抽油煙機吸油煙勁? 嘈都無咩所謂 煮飯都係一陣 最緊要抽到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋因為屋企廚房細 應該都係買番傳統台式 直接係部機頂裝排煙管屈出去<br />\n呢種<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/235653_1167610aa17b0813233fe82d99403e41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F235653_1167610aa17b0813233fe82d99403e41.jpg&h=7a372365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔可以太高<br />\n姐係呢種唔得<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/06/235720_36bec2b148637723165ed9d633a7d980.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F06%2F235720_36bec2b148637723165ed9d633a7d980.jpg&h=2960ab90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd886ded550dc2339e91ae03e532ca22ccb764da","tid":426500,"uid":7576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"推推推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce7ca8d6d0fc38903c0f90366dfa3ed59f9d51e","tid":426500,"uid":7576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:04